          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Government relocations:</strong> We have extensive experience with APS and contractor
            relocations. We understand the timelines and requirements of government moves.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-brand-dark mb-12">ACT Coverage</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-100">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4">Canberra Districts</h3>
